The '''''Kratak''''' was a [[Matalok|cruiser analog]] used by the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] during the [[Battle of Coruscant (Yuuzhan Vong War)|Battle of Coruscant]]. [[Warmaster]] [[Tsavong Lah]] transferred his flag to the ''Kratak'', after the destruction of the ''[[Sunulok]]''.

